Class LruObjectMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object

    java.lang.Iterable<org.mini2Dx.gdx.utils.ObjectMap.Entry<K,V>>

    ConcurrentLruObjectMap

    public class LruObjectMap<K,V>
extends org.mini2Dx.gdx.utils.ObjectMap<K,V>
    Extends ObjectMap to implement least-recently used capabilities. Once the specified maximum capacity is reached, the key that has been used the least is removed from the map.
